article.description: Xavier Johnson poured in 35 points and Chicago State rolled to a 103-60 victory over NAIA member Judson College on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Johnson scores 35, Chicago State routs Judson 103-60
article.linkText: Johnson scores 35, Chicago State routs Judson 103-60
article.story: CHICAGO -- Xavier Johnson poured in 35 points and Chicago State rolled to a 103-60 victory over NAIA member Judson College on Tuesday night. The Cougars jumped out to a 20-point halftime lead and outscored the Eagles 57-34 after intermission. Chicago will host Loyola Maryland on Saturday.
